QuestData.Title: Questioning Reethe
QuestData.Description: It took a long time, but I found Reethe. He hide good for a human.$b$bOgron worried that he might be crazy after so much time in swamp. You come with me for we go get answers from him.
QuestData.LogDescription: Go with Ogron to speak with Reethe.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Krog at Brackenwall Village in Dustwallow Marsh.
QuestData.RewardText: Hmph. It is good that Reethe will no longer be lurking around the swamp, but it is a shame that humans are built so frail that he could not recover from a little arrow wound.$b$bIt seems that this thread of the mystery has led nowhere, and we must look elsewhere.
